- @page_title = 'Edit Offer'

- if @offer.featured?
  %h3 Featured Installs
  %p.description
    Featured Installs let you buy premium views for your app offer, such as being displayed full-screen when an app is launched. Like Pay-Per-Install, you only pay when a user installs your app.
  %p.description
    Enter your bid per featured install below. The minimum bid is 100% of the purchase price for paid apps, or $0.65 for free apps. Higher bids will fetch more installs.
- elsif !@offer.rewarded?
  %h3 Non-Rewarded Installs
  %p.description
    PUT A DESCRIPTION HERE YO.
  %p.description
    Enter your bid per non-rewarded install below. The minimum bid is $0.50.
- else
  %h3 Pay-Per-Install
  %p.description
    Pay-Per-Install lets you buy a set number of incentivized installations for your app. Only pay when a user installs and runs your application.
  %p.description
    Enter your bid per install below. The minimum bid is 50% of the purchase price for paid apps, or $0.35 for free apps. 
    Higher bids will result in more installs.

= render('apps/offers_shared/scheduling') if @offer.tapjoy_enabled?
= render('apps/offers_shared/form', :featured => @offer.featured?)
